According to the Nielsen cabinet, Google is the most used [[search engine]] on the web with a 54% market share, ahead of [[Yahoo!]] (23%) and [[Windows Live Search]] (13%). However, independent estimates from popular sites indicate that more than 80% of search referrals come from Google, with Yahoo! a distant second and Windows Live Search occupying barely 5%. The Google search engine receives about a billion search requests per day.
